      <div>
        <p style="font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin:0 0 6px 0;">MCP standardizes agent-tool interaction</p>
        <p style="font-size:17px; color:#94a3b8; margin:0;">One protocol for tools, resources, prompts, and completions — across every IDE and agent</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:20px;">
      <div class="vis-step" style="background:rgba(96,165,250,0.2); border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.3); color:#60a5fa; width:52px; height:52px; font-size:22px;">2</div>
      <div>
        <p style="font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin:0 0 6px 0;">Context engineering is the new skill to master</p>
        <p style="font-size:17px; color:#94a3b8; margin:0;">Steering with rules files, managing context windows, and using subagents for segmentation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:20px;">
      <div class="vis-step" style="background:rgba(168,85,247,0.2); border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.3); color:#c084fc; width:52px; height:52px; font-size:22px;">3</div>
      <div>
        <p style="font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin:0 0 6px 0;">Guardrails are non-negotiable for AI-generated code</p>
        <p style="font-size:17px; color:#94a3b8; margin:0;">Security, quality, performance, and architecture — enforced deterministically with hooks</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:20px;">
      <div class="vis-step" style="background:rgba(251,191,36,0.2); border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.3); color:#fbbf24; width:52px; height:52px; font-size:22px;">4</div>
      <div>
        <p style="font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin:0 0 6px 0;">Secure your agent toolchain like any supply chain</p>
        <p style="font-size:17px; color:#94a3b8; margin:0;">Allowlist MCP servers, audit tool usage, sandbox execution, vet dependencies</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:20px;">
      <div class="vis-step" style="background:rgba(248,113,113,0.2); border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.3); color:#f87171; width:52px; height:52px; font-size:22px;">5</div>
