        <p style="font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin:0 0 6px 0;">Policy as Code + AI agents = DevSecOps at scale</p>
        <p style="font-size:17px; color:#94a3b8; margin:0;">Semgrep, Conftest, hooks, and agent review create a layered defense that continuously improves</p>
